{"type": "article", "id": 17425, "title": "方形储物柜", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-12T06:43:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 64, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606153507F78JYgKkum96LpOr.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这些黑白灰的方形储物柜来自丹麦的设计公司 by Lassens。方形柜子的正中间有个做拉手的小黑点，让这组极简的柜子带了点诙谐。大小不同型号和不同颜色可以自由组合，悬挂在墙上是有艺术气息的墙面装饰，也能在下面多安装一个支架成为茶几或者床头柜。柜子可单独售卖，<a href=\"http://bylassen.com/shop/frame-64c1.html\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261445143SRpshiOcBa19gKv.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"1280\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144515mbtkHavZMSJO9Biy.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144515KSCs7T6j8u2W4oLN.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"767\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.27833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144516IRa3h4qSrzEHcdwQ.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144516kYHG3Iz08ZWfD1rx.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}